        {
            "title": "Polaris股價飆升10%,公司無懼關稅逆風",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wn.rYUWN1hqAlMLBctbzFQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB0507V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Polaris Inc. (NYSE:PII) 股價週四大漲10%,此前該公司表示,近期關稅政策變化不會對其3月3日發布的2026年財務指引產生重大影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家動力運動產品製造商表示,預計關稅變化(不包括潛在退款)對其全年展望不會產生重大影響。此前,競爭對手BRP Inc. (NASDAQ:DOO) 週三因美國關稅政策變化而暫停其2027財年指引,導致Polaris股價下跌。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7621d93c-c1b4-3a15-86c0-9648737e0647-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Polaris強調其作為唯一一家總部位於美國的大型動力運動產品公司的地位,並擁有大量本土製造業務。該公司在阿拉巴馬州、印第安納州和明尼蘇達州設有生產設施。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示,正持續加強與國內供應商的關係。Polaris計劃於4月28日週二的第一季度財報電話會議上提供更多細節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/polaris%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8710-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%80%86%E9%A2%A8-155828953.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 00:28:04",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "海灣國家和歐洲官員據悉認為美伊和談需六個月 呼籲延長停火",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情官員稱，一些海灣國家和歐洲領導人認為，美伊達成和平協議大約需要六個月時間，交戰方應將停火延長至覆蓋這段時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的知情官員表示，這些領導人希望立即重開霍爾木茲海峽以恢復能源流動，並在私下警告稱，如果到下個月仍未實現，全球可能出現糧食危機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他們還表示，如果戰爭持續更長時間，能源價格可能進一步上漲。布倫特周四上漲約3.5%，至每桶98美元上方。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情官員稱，海灣國家認為伊朗仍有意發展核武器，美以轟炸伊朗後並沒有改變這一點。因此，他們認為任何和平協議都應禁止伊朗進行鈾濃縮或擁有遠程彈道飛彈。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-12d7ab75-a285-36e7-81dd-221272eba994-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，這些官員表示，海灣國家領導人大多反對重啟戰事，希望美國尋求與伊朗進行外交斡旋。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美伊考慮延長停火 川普稱以黎同意停火10天 (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沙烏地、卡達、科威特、阿曼和巴林政府發言人未立即回應彭博的置評請求。阿聯酋外交部引述4月8日的聲明，稱必須「無條件重開霍爾木茲海峽」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯酋的聲明「強調需要採取全面且持續的方式，應對伊朗帶來的各類威脅，包括其核能力、彈道飛彈、無人機、軍事能力以及相關代理人和恐怖組織。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US-Iran Deal Will Take Months, Gulf and European Officials Say</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%87%E9%9C%80%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB-165424786.html",
