        {
            "title": "德國企業投資轉向中國等亞洲市場 對美投資意願下降",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"DIHK\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"837\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/L.dJ2QyUNjNhnLy_CWCh1w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ab6eedcf47e5b05c8d3ee0cddfe2b15f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">DIHK</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 行業游說團體德國工商總會（DIHK）調查顯示，由於美國總統唐納德·川普的關稅政策，投資美國的德國企業數量正在減少，投資重心正轉向中國和其他亞洲國家。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DIHK周四表示，在約1,700家受訪製造商中，44%的企業表示計畫在美國投資，較2025年調查下降4個百分點，為新冠疫情以來首次顯著下滑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">34%的受訪企業將中國列為投資目標，高於此前的31%；對於不含中國的亞太地區，這一比例躍升5個百分點，至26%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5c4fec3d-e42f-314d-a553-27f09e582865-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與美國的貿易爭端正在加劇不確定性，促使企業推遲決策，」DIHK對外貿易主管Volker Treier表示。他指出，在亞洲，企業越來越轉向在當地生產並銷售產品，尤其是在中國和印度市場。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"837\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jUhZ6PzF2QvTa9H4dYQj2Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/57dc3bfd33a6f43eb9789c4c5077da21\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐元區仍然是德國對外投資最重要的地區，且優勢明顯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「歐元區的穩定性、統一的內部市場以及共同貨幣，為企業提供了可靠的制度環境，」DIHK報告稱，「在地緣政治不確定性加劇的背景下，這一點在投資決策中尤為重要，不容低估。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題German Companies Increasingly Favor Asia Over US Investments</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Zoe Schneeweiss.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
